Mu mwaka wa 2015, Perezida Pierre Nkurunziza yatangaje ko ashaka manda ya gatatu, bituma abantu benshi batavuga rumwe n’imvururu .  yafashije gutsinda umugambi wo guhirika ubutegetsi bwa Nkurunziza muri Gicurasi 2015 kandi yabonaga ko ari we wateguye igitero cyo guhashya abigaragambyaga.   Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu washinjaga Nshimirimana kuba "umwe mu bantu bakomeye ba perezida."  Nshimirimana yagize uruhare runini mu gihe imyigaragambyo n’imyigaragambyo yo kwamagana Nkurunziza byakomeje hagati muri 2015. Nk’uko Carina Tertsakian wo muri Human Rights Watch abivuga, "Nubwo cyangwa wenda kubera izina rye ry'ubugome, Adolphe yabonaga ko adakoraho, nta muntu n'umwe wari ufite ubutwari bwo gutinyuka, cyangwa ngo amutange ibitekerezo, ngo abimubaze." 

Ku ya 4 Kanama 2015, Nkurunziza yategetse abapolisi gushaka abicanyi ba Nshimirimana, mu minsi icumi bari bahagarariwe nk'umuntu w’iburyo bwa perezida. 

Kanama 2015. Nshimirimana yarapfuye abandi batatu barakomereka bikabije .

Ku ya 13 Ukuboza 2016, abapolisi bo mu Burundi batangaje ko umwe mu bakekwaho kuba barishe Nshimirimana yatorotse gereza yica umuzamu.
